ol.li:
Add the desired dnsmasq_dns_servers items by modifying the
                        value field with the IP address of your DNS server.
                    Multiple DNS servers can be specified as a comma separated list.
Your JSON
                        should appear similar to the
                    following:{"dhcp_agent":
    {"config":
        [
            {"section":"DEFAULT",
                "values":
                    [
                        {"option":"dhcp_delete_namespaces","value":"True"},
                        {"option":"dnsmasq_dns_servers", "value":"0.0.0.0"}
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    }
